Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:12.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest are sent to a forbidden place,\N and they learn its secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:15.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:17.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Ruins.
